name: Kyberdyne
public_notice: Kyberdyne has migrated from the old contract to new one. For more info, refer to their Medium article.

description.en: Kyberdyne is a DBG (Deck-Building Game) with a Rogue-like mechanism built by an AAA game studio. Kyberdyne brings high quality gaming elements to blockchain game players, enabling them to build their own dream team and earn unique rewards.
